cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper proposes a method for event lifetime estimation and disparity estimation for stereo event-cameras, which is a topic related to computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves estimation and association of events, which can be related to robotics and control (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper proposes a method for single shot event lifetime and disparity estimation, which can be related to neural networks and machine learning (cs.NE), as well as statistical learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
